# ============================================================
# 1. PROJECT OVERVIEW
# ============================================================

# SENTINEL is a self-healing support chatbot for EdTech platforms.
# Core loop: question → vector search → if low confidence → clarifying question
# → LLM synthesizes FAQ → saves to ChromaDB permanently → streams answer.
#
# Stack:
#   Backend  → FastAPI (Python 3.10+), ChromaDB, sentence-transformers, Groq Cloud
#   Frontend → React 18 + Vite, Vanilla CSS, Native WebSocket API
#   LLMs     → llama-3.3-70b-versatile (synthesis), llama-3.1-8b-instant (streaming)
#   Embeddings → all-MiniLM-L6-v2 (local, ~90MB)

# ============================================================
# 2. DIRECTORY STRUCTURE
# ============================================================

# /
# ├── backend/
# │   ├── main.py          ← FastAPI app, WebSocket handler, REST endpoints
# │   ├── rag.py           ← ChromaDB client, search_kb(), is_duplicate(), upsert_entry()
# │   ├── synthesis.py     ← Groq client, generate_clarifying_question(), synthesize_faq(), stream_answer()
# │   ├── seed_data.py     ← 15 seed FAQs, seed_if_empty()
